Question.Subject: what does false mean on the martha stewart web page?
Question.Content: i try to get easter egg designs on martha stewart.com but the screen goes blank and says false on it what is that and how can i stop it
Question.ChosenAnswer:
Maybe there was a problem with the web server. But it appears to work fine for me. Try going to http://www.marthastewart.com/photogallery/easter-eggs
If you still get "False" then you might have a problem with your PC such as a virus.
